- Refactored line-item CRUD to persist applies-to via junction rows (dedupe + sort order), plus eager loading with `selectinload`, in [backend/app/services/module.py](/Users/ainunnajib/dynaplan/backend/app/services/module.py#L76).
- Added efficient query support and endpoint `GET /dimensions/{dimension_id}/line-items` in [backend/app/api/module.py](/Users/ainunnajib/dynaplan/backend/app/api/module.py#L190).
